{
    "id": "welcome/run-tests",
    "title": "Run the Test Suite",
    "description": "Learn how to run DSPACE's automated tests to ensure your changes are correct.",
    "image": "/assets/quests/run_tests_terminal_dashboard.jpg",
    "npc": "/assets/npc/dChat.jpg",
    "start": "start",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "id": "start",
            "text": "Testing catches regressions early and keeps reviews fast. Learn the commands, then we’ll set up your local run.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "guide",
                    "text": "Show me the command list."
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "quiz-1",
                    "text": "Quiz me."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "guide",
            "text": "Use npm run qa:smoke for a fast sanity check (type-check, link-check, item validation, CI-parity tests without Playwright). Use npm run test:pr (or npm test) for the full pre-PR suite with grouped Playwright E2E. For targeted content checks, run npm test -- questQuality or npm test -- itemQuality.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "quiz-1",
                    "text": "Got it—quiz me."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "quiz-1",
            "text": "Which command is the fastest sanity check before a longer run?",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "quiz-2",
                    "text": "npm run qa:smoke"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "quiz-1-wrong",
                    "text": "npm run test:pr"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "quiz-1-wrong",
                    "text": "npm run lint"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "quiz-1-wrong",
            "text": "Close, but qa:smoke is the quick sanity pass before the full suite.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "start",
                    "text": "Back to start"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "quiz-2",
            "text": "Which command runs the full pre-PR suite with grouped Playwright E2E?",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "quiz-3",
                    "text": "npm run test:pr"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "quiz-2-wrong",
                    "text": "npm run qa:smoke"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "quiz-2-wrong",
                    "text": "npm run build"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "quiz-2-wrong",
            "text": "qa:smoke is the fast pass, but test:pr is the full pre-PR suite with grouped Playwright.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "start",
                    "text": "Reset and try again"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "quiz-3",
            "text": "What should you run before opening a PR?",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "quiz-4",
                    "text": "npm test (same as npm run test:pr)"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "quiz-3-wrong",
                    "text": "npm run lint"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "quiz-3-wrong",
                    "text": "npm run qa:smoke"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "quiz-3-wrong",
            "text": "Lint and qa:smoke are useful, but the pre-PR expectation is npm test (test:pr).",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "start",
                    "text": "Try again"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "quiz-4",
            "text": "If Playwright browsers are missing, how do you skip E2E tests?",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "prep-repo",
                    "text": "SKIP_E2E=1 npm test"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "quiz-4-wrong",
                    "text": "E2E_SKIP=1 npm test"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "quiz-4-wrong",
                    "text": "npm test --no-e2e"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "quiz-4-wrong",
            "text": "Use the documented flag: SKIP_E2E=1 npm test.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "start",
                    "text": "Back to start"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
